{"tid":2428223,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(網吧)一人一個網吧打機趣事!!","createTime":"2021-03-01T11:41:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T14:02:14.000Z","uid":119688,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"b07014c680c052b36463806c6987d0e00091d414","tid":2428223,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T11:41:00.000Z","msg":"當年中學放學狗沖去網吧打機<br />\n最鐘意玩cs1.5<br />\n好記得要連線玩<br />\n只可以同一網吧既人玩<br />\n連唔出公海既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當年我專玩ak,槍法如神,真心準<br />\n一槍一頭,殺到對面條mk金毛拍枱仲車左隻滑鼠埋黎<br />\n仲話要吹雞打尻我叫我唔好走<br />\n仲問我讀邊個學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我呢世仔最驚就係依次個人震哂<br />\n真係嚇到尻都縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後同佢講左幾十次sorry<br />\n仲幫佢加左個杯麵先走得<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b610fe06997a1ee2f33306a14daa7c23b1cf23f1","tid":2428223,"uid":38707,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T11:42:08.000Z","msg":"聽到有人做愛<br />\n大叫：椰汁炸豬扒！椰汁炸豬扒！"},{"pid":"5fd59b9b2f69de7af4a154958c685dedba62da78","tid":2428223,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T11:42:31.000Z","msg":"如果再比我見到佢 我一定打到佢仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"650c6f43c8be358d1ce716f7636761ee11ffaeb9","tid":2428223,"uid":125760,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T11:43:10.000Z","msg":"樓主真係幾老，我都係玩開cs1.6 你玩1.5"},{"pid":"5f4b0ca9a2ad1e8b8d55e706e24e73829fa093e3","tid":2428223,"uid":189911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-